  "detailed_description": "Take the loot, pirates!<br><br>- Victory rests on the berry in your hand!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918150/extras/dd8de79b5af95f365ab56fe64ceb12b7.poster.avif?t=1762511808\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918150/extras/dd8de79b5af95f365ab56fe64ceb12b7.webm?t=1762511808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Bounty Rush is the first ONE PIECE 4 vs 4 multiplayer team action game.<br>In this game, working with your team is the key to victory!<br>Compete in real-time, with complete synchronization, against an enemy team and aim to steal their berries!<br><br>- The world of ONE PIECE has been transformed into a 3D battlefield!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918150/extras/53e25c3e856bceac0db0716a81f8b0ca.avif?t=1762511808\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918150/extras_big/53e25c3e856bceac0db0716a81f8b0ca.avif?t=1762511808 width=800 height=450 /></span><br>The stages are filled with items that give you and your team an advantage, as well as obstacles that get in your way.<br>Use whatever you can get your hands on and lead your team to victory!<br><br>- Emerge victorious using distinctive ONE PIECE characters in Team Battle!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918150/extras/e0a0fc3fb2c51afd9bdceafae40ebaac.poster.avif?t=1762511808\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918150/extras/e0a0fc3fb2c51afd9bdceafae40ebaac.webm?t=1762511808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918150/extras/a354b4ee2f37356af2eb1407e64a3f81.poster.avif?t=1762511808\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918150/extras/a354b4ee2f37356af2eb1407e64a3f81.webm?t=1762511808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>In this mode, you can control popular ONE PIECE characters and battle against rival teams.<br>Characters have different strengths too: those who excel at advancing the frontlines and those who are better at taking the defensive in the rear.<br>Pick your playstyle and charge into battle!",
  "about_the_game": "Take the loot, pirates!<br><br>- Victory rests on the berry in your hand!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918150/extras/dd8de79b5af95f365ab56fe64ceb12b7.poster.avif?t=1762511808\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918150/extras/dd8de79b5af95f365ab56fe64ceb12b7.webm?t=1762511808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Bounty Rush is the first ONE PIECE 4 vs 4 multiplayer team action game.<br>In this game, working with your team is the key to victory!<br>Compete in real-time, with complete synchronization, against an enemy team and aim to steal their berries!<br><br>- The world of ONE PIECE has been transformed into a 3D battlefield!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918150/extras/53e25c3e856bceac0db0716a81f8b0ca.avif?t=1762511808\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918150/extras_big/53e25c3e856bceac0db0716a81f8b0ca.avif?t=1762511808 width=800 height=450 /></span><br>The stages are filled with items that give you and your team an advantage, as well as obstacles that get in your way.<br>Use whatever you can get your hands on and lead your team to victory!<br><br>- Emerge victorious using distinctive ONE PIECE characters in Team Battle!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918150/extras/e0a0fc3fb2c51afd9bdceafae40ebaac.poster.avif?t=1762511808\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918150/extras/e0a0fc3fb2c51afd9bdceafae40ebaac.webm?t=1762511808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918150/extras/a354b4ee2f37356af2eb1407e64a3f81.poster.avif?t=1762511808\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2918150/extras/a354b4ee2f37356af2eb1407e64a3f81.webm?t=1762511808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>In this mode, you can control popular ONE PIECE characters and battle against rival teams.<br>Characters have different strengths too: those who excel at advancing the frontlines and those who are better at taking the defensive in the rear.<br>Pick your playstyle and charge into battle!",
